{"tid":2031893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得好驚嘅你入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-05-23T17:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T03:21:33.000Z","uid":347687,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92185664e9623cc49ccc7a3ef060fec074b5cc56","tid":2031893,"uid":347687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:15:26.000Z","msg":"盡自己所能，做自己所想<br />\nYou are not alone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗暴之戰由上年開始<br />\n無論係和理非定勇武手足<br />\n你上街，你抗爭<br />\n相信大家都已經做咗能力所及嘅事<br />\n<br />\n可能你有包袱 唔可以義無反顧咁企出嚟<br />\n可能你會好驚 唔知自己承唔承擔到個後果<br />\n但係有咩恐怖得過<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">永續嘅恐懼</span></strong></span>？<br />\n<br />\n你依一刻擔心嘅嘢<br />\n可能會成為你有生之年嘅惡夢<br />\n你寧願過住日後都擔驚受怕嘅日子<br />\n定係同其他手足一齊面對眼前嘅現實？<br />\n<br />\n香港人始終心存希望<br />\n尚存一息都唔會放棄<br />\n<br />\n希望明天524見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3uYPiDn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3uYPiDn.jpg&h=975368a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UE0YWp3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUE0YWp3.jpg&h=e147ec4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Smn4RYo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmn4RYo.jpg&h=74007479&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"038333107a5d3d08b6d9a9126336ccc72ae706c9","tid":2031893,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T18:20:18.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落"},{"pid":"e83778cc9070e764cc0636b20854290be80e2a1f","tid":2031893,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T18:40:25.000Z","msg":"驚到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727edb7cfdff0f17eba9ead2a8341f40e5b43f96","tid":2031893,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score